metadata.name: Shaman's Hyperspace Voyage
metadata.description:
This artwork depicts an Amazonian shaman entering a visionary state and traveling in his astral body to hyperspace, where he merges with the spirit of Pachamama, who is the goddess of earth revered by the indigenous people of the Amazonian Andes.

10% profit from the sale will be donated to andesamazonfund.org

Collector will also receive a signed print.

1/1 Edition | 4583x4000 | PNG
